Package com.empirilytics.qatch.analyzers

Interface MetricsAnalyzer

All Known Implementing Classes:
CKJMAnalyzer, CKPMAnalyzer
public interface MetricsAnalyzer
This is an abstract class that describes the minimum functionality that an Analyzer should have in order to work properly.

e.g. PMDAnalyzer, CKJMAnalyzer etc.
